  <brief_title>Effect of Topiroxostat on Urinary Albumin Excretion Early Stage Diabetic Nephropathy and Hyperuricemia With or Without Gout</brief_title>
  <acronym>UPWARD</acronym>
  <official_title>Effect of Topiroxostat on Urinary Albumin Excretion in Patients With eARly Stage Diabetic Nephropathy and Hyperuricemia With or Without Gout: a Randomized, Placebo-controlled, Double-blind Phase 2a Trial (UPWARD).</official_title>
