  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diabetes patients

          -  Clinically or pathologically diagnosed diabetic nephropathy

          -  Hyperuricemic or gout patients

          -  Estimated glomerular filtration rate (eGFR) &gt;= 30 mL/min/1.73m^2 and urine albumin
             creatinine ratio (UACR) greater than or equal to 45 and less than 300 mg/g

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient has known non-diabetic nephropathy (other than nephrosclerosis)
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
